<arggraph id="micro_c056" topic_id="promote_recycling_by_bottle_deposit" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[All states should adopt a deposit on soft drink bottles and cans]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[because it greatly incentives recycling.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[The five or ten cent deposit is noticeable and serves as a reminder of recycling during checkout.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[Once you have collected a bag or two full of cans and bottles, returning those cans and bottles is worth $5-$15, a meaningful amount of money for many people and families.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[Recycling is vital]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[and incentivizing it in this simple way works.]]></edu>
